@SamBFarkas I recently had my first and was terrified because I’m claustrophobic. I just kept my eyes shut and pretended I was Murderbot. It helped. 

The machine also slid around a lot, so I never felt like I was “stuck inside.”

In all, the buildup was much worse than the experience, IMHO.

@Glenn_sccc Yes, first time hitting double digits. 

If more than one agent is interested once they have read the entire book, then I will have to choose among them. 

Bidding wars are for publishers. That will be the next step, if we’re lucky. 😌

